    "summary": "The user asks the assistant to manage a cluster maintenance schedule involving the permanent decommissioning of specific hardware nodes. Upon learning that the decommissioning will interrupt critical research, the assistant proposes two solutions: migrating the workload or temporarily suspending the decommissioning/placing nodes in \"quarantine.\"",
